  "body": "### Description\r\nAdd mention, add text, hit backspace, click just before the mention's last character -> Mention is deleted.\r\nRoot cause: StatusChatInput onCursorPositionChanged processes text based on last known key used. In this case backspace, even if the cursor was moved by mouse.\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/47811206/207095155-5e551df4-5cf6-4edb-9175-7bb18461413b.mov\r\n\r\nReproduced on MacOs",
